                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wl-6-86h-F4">赤背松柏根短影剪輯</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-box-container text-box-container-info">
        <div class="text-box--species">
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    家族
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    黃頷蛇科，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natricinae" lang="en-US">Natricinae</a> 亞種              
                    <br>
                    Colubridae, subfamily <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natricinae" lang="en-US">Natricinae</a>  
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    最大體長
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    60 cm
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    台灣棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    主要分布在北台灣海拔500 - 1000 m的地方。瀕危。(<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://archive.zo.ntu.edu.tw/rept_map.asp?rept_id=R0072">線上分布地圖</a>) 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    世界棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    台灣特有種 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    外觀描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    Small snake; total length up to 60 cm. There are 17-19 rows of scales, all are strongly keeled. Head is slightly triangular; body is slender; tail is very long. Eye is medium to large; iris is brown, dappled with coarse black pigment and pupil is round, jet black with red margin. Tongue is black, with whitish diverging point. Upper head is uniformly brown with a white spot above the base of jaw. The labials are generally white and may show dark sutures; there is a black stripe extending posteriorly from eye to posterior part of upper labials and connecting with the black stripe on upper body. Upper body and tail are distinctly marked with seven longitudinal stripes. From vertebral ridge to each side of body, they are: one broad stripe of dark brown with dark margins bilaterally, one dorsolateral stripe of yellow to tan (white on neck), one narrow stripe of dark brown to black, and one broad stripe of red (white on neck). Ventral head is white. Ventral body and tail are light yellow; the red flanks of upper body extend onto outer quarter or fifth of ventral scales and the small black spots near latero-ventral junction form a longitudinal stripe. Anal scale is divided and subcaudals are paired. 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    生態描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text"> 	
                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        日行性為主的蛇種，偶爾會在夜間出沒。喜歡棲息在潮濕的山區地帶。以獵取青蛙、蟾蜍與蝌蚪維生，曾經被人發現在離地面1.6m高的樹洞吞食艾氏樹蛙(<span lang="en-US"><i>Chirixalus eiffingeri</i></span>)的蝌蚪。母蛇每次產卵約會產下3枚長形卵，每枚約長4cm寬1cm。
                    </div>
                    金絲蛇的棲地目前已經遭受到嚴重的破壞與人為的入侵。往往發現時都是被車輾過慘死在馬路上的屍體。 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    學名與俗名
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">                
                    <span lang="en-US"><i>Amphiesma</i></span>: 來自希臘語有 "服裝, 祭帶" 的意思，轉為白話就是"腹鏈"，用來形容牠腹鱗兩側的鏈狀花紋。類似的還有 <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link--species" href="amphiesma-stolatum_zh.html" lang="en-US">Amphiesma stolatum(花浪蛇)</a>。
                    miyajimae: 紀念日本人宮島氏(<span lang="en-US">Miyajima</span>)於1928年5月在台北採獲的模式標本。
                    金絲蛇，宮島氏腹鏈蛇，台北腹鏈蛇。 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    附註
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">       
                金絲蛇(<span lang="en-US"><i>Amphiesma miyajimae</i></span>)形似 羽鳥氏帶紋赤蛇 (<span lang="en-US"><i>Sinomicrurus hatori</i></span>) 與 梭德氏帶紋赤蛇(<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link--species" href="sinomicrurus-sauteri_zh.html" lang="en-US">Sinomicrurus sauteri</a>). 不過其實不難區分，羽鳥氏與梭德氏頸部是一條白色帶狀斑，而金絲蛇則是兩塊白色圓點。                
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    相關連結
                </div>
                <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://e-info.org.tw/node/40019">特有生物的哀愁 金絲蛇 - 轉自 環境資訊中心</a></li>
                    <li lang="en-US"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://reptile-database.reptarium.cz/species.php?genus=Amphiesma&species=miyajimae">Reptile Database</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="translator-name">翻譯:周信甫</div>

        </div>
    </div>

